snippet.title: Project Mansion - Reveal Teaser
snippet.description:
In a spiraling descent into madness, a broke journalist must confront ancient enigmas, survive eldritch horrors in a damned mansion, and face his own fractured existence.

▶️Follow us for more updates on Project Mansion!

- - - -
Project Mansion (working title) is in development state. Anything in the trailer is a work in progress and a subject of change in the future.
